rules.description: Change left control + left gui + e TO mouse button 4
Simultaneous up and down keys TO mouse button 4
Change right_option key to Meta key
Change caps_lock to control
Change right_command + wasd to arrow keys
Change right_command + pl;' to arrow keys
Change right_command + [],return to volume controls
Change right_command + <>? to music controls
Change right_command + uio to print-scroll-pause
Change right_command + j to tilde
KBP V60 - Bottom Right Mods to Meta Keys
For Filco only: Swap command and option keys
Post Escape if grave_accent_and_tilde (backtick) is pressed alone; post grave_accent (backtick) if Option + grave_accent_and_tilde is pressed.
